Don't.

287
00:22:25,500 --> 00:22:27,749
Just lay it down then
where he can't get it.

288
00:22:27,833 --> 00:22:29,332
Before someone gets hurt.

289
00:22:31,083 --> 00:22:35,624
Sorry, I'm going to give it to him.
