486
00:33:23,625 --> 00:33:25,582
I can't think
of an example right now but...

487
00:33:25,666 --> 00:33:27,165
Great. Thank you.

488
00:33:31,375 --> 00:33:35,249
Now.
Now you're being pleasant.

489
00:33:38,500 --> 00:33:39,540
