you might be up against.

697
00:49:17,208 --> 00:49:18,707
Okay. Go on.

698
00:49:18,791 --> 00:49:22,499
Well, I can't offer you health cover
or a pension scheme,

699
00:49:22,583 --> 00:49:24,249
